title: You Get A Baby! And You Get A Baby!
itunes:title: You Get A Baby! And You Get A Baby!
description:
THU 11/17 - Nick Cannon stops by The Breakfast Club and confirms his baby-on-the-way, explains why he'll never name drop his sexual partners again, gives his reaction to Mariah's availability, elaborates on his "Too Broke to Vote" campaign, talks "King of the Dancehall" movie and his new mixtape "The Gospel of Ike Turn Up"!
